  "detailed_description": "Point and meow. 3D hidden cat game. These creatures have been turned into stone. Find and save them all.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA short point and click exploration, with hints and references to my hometown in Australia. <br />\r\nSlight puzzling and extra hidden objects. <br />\r\nRelaxing with slight moody vibes.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSolo dev, 3d models, and art by me. Game made in Godot.<br />\r\nThis game was made for a friend, you can play it too.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWorking on additional free areas, secrets, and more polishing. This is my first game thank you.",
